  "title": "Accountant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Accounting & Finance</strong></p><p>- Handle full set of accounts including AP, AR, GL, bankreconciliation and month-end closing</p><p>- Prepare monthly financial statements, management reportsand cash flow forecasts</p><p>- Monitor daily sales takings, credit card settlements, andmarketplace payouts (Shopee/Lazada, etc.)</p><p>- Track inventory costing, stock valuation, and cost ofgoods sold (COGS)</p><p>- Process staff claims, petty cash, and supplier payments ina timely manner</p><p><strong>Tax & Compliance</strong></p><p>- Prepare and submit GST returns and ensure compliance withIRAS requirements</p><p>- Assist in corporate tax computation and liaise with taxagents/auditors</p><p>- Ensure proper documentation and filing in accordance withstatutory requirements</p><p><strong>Retail Operations Support</strong></p><p>- Reconcile POS system sales with accounting records</p><p>- Manage supplier invoices, debit notes, credit notes, andprice protection claims</p><p>- Support consignment, trade-in, and promotional accountingmatters</p><p>- Monitor inventory discrepancies and work closely withoperations team</p><p><strong>Audit & Reporting</strong></p><p>- Assist in annual audit preparation and provide supportingschedules</p><p>- Maintain proper accounting records and internal controls</p><p>- Prepare ad-hoc financial analysis and reports as requiredby management</p><p><strong>Requirements / Qualifications</strong></p><p>- Diploma / Degree in Accounting, Finance, or related field</p><p>- Minimum 2–3 years of relevant accounting experience(retail experience preferred)</p><p>- Knowledge of GST and Singapore accounting standards</p><p>- Familiar with accounting software (e.g. Xero, QuickBooks,MYOB, SAP) and Excel</p><p>- Experience handling inventory-heavy retail businesses isan advantage</p><p><strong>Skills & Attributes</strong></p><p>- Detail-oriented, organised, and able to meet deadlines</p><p>- Able to work independently and handle multiple tasks</p><p>- Good communication skills to liaise with suppliers andinternal teams</p><p>- High level of integrity and confidentiality</p><p><strong>Working Environment</strong></p><p>- Retail camera business with fast-moving inventory andpromotional cycles</p><p>- Office-based with occasional coordination with retailoutlets<br /><br /><br /><u><strong>Singaporean and PR only</strong></u></p>",
